Title: 165: Giving Back to the Data Science Community
Description:
In this episode of the SuperDataScience Podcast, I chat with the Founder of Business Science, Matt Dancho. You will hear what the business and data science industries could learn and benefit from each other, know the many different ways how to give back to the data science community, and get insights on becoming the greatest data scientist you could ever be.


If you enjoyed this episode, check out show notes, resources, and more at www.superdatascience.com/165
